2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a new type of computer vision task that requires advanced AI algorithms to detect tiny vehicles efficiently. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper may use machine learning techniques to train the model for detecting tiny moving vehicles. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper may propose a framework that can be used in autonomous vehicles or drones for detecting small moving vehicles in satellite videos. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and processing satellite videos, which is a type of multimedia data.
